1980;;Stardust Memories;;American;;Woody Allen;;Woody Allen, Charlotte Rampling, Jessica Harper;;comedy, drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Stardust_Memories;;The film follows famous filmmaker Sandy Bates, who is plagued by fans who prefer his "earlier, funnier movies" to his more recent artistic efforts, while he tries to reconcile his conflicting attraction to two very different women: the earnest intellectual Daisy and the more maternal Isobel. Meanwhile, he is also haunted by memories of his ex-girlfriend, the unstable Dorrie.